## Visual spec (secplus-pbq-page.css + `.pbq-bct-sim`)

| Element | Style |
|---------|--------|
| Logo watermark | 10% opacity, centered (sim pattern) |
| Nav links | BCT sim blue (`#005ecb` / `rgba(0,100,230,0.92)`) |
| Action buttons | BCT sim blue — same as `simulation-*.html` |
| Exhibit launchers | Blue artifact tiles in `.pbq-exhibit-launchers` |
| Draggable tokens | Light blue `#cfe9ff` |
| Drop slots | Light blue `#dbeafe`, dashed `#93c5fd` |
| Layer / timeline blocks | Light purple `#f3e8ff` inside `.layer-list-box` (map rows or timeline steps) |
| Correct / incorrect slots | Green / red (unchanged) |

## Interaction

- Drag-and-drop + tap-to-pick (click token, click slot)
- `#bank` + `.drop-slot[data-target="token-id"]` — slot `data-target` must match token `data-value`
- Shuffle bank on load and reset
- Inline script at bottom of page (copy from reference neighbor)

## Chain navigation

Wire **Back / Next** in the scenario folder (`PBQ_Production/{scenario-slug}/` while building, `SEC+_PBQ/` when published). Last page: disabled Next or portal. Update the previous page’s Next when adding a slug.

## Sourcing workflow

After shipping a new page, log accepted concepts in `marketing-vault/11-question-sourcing/pbq/secplus-pbq-not-in-bct.md`. Compare bank: `npm run secplus:pbq-monthly`.

## Answer verification

Verify against **CompTIA Tier A / SY0-701 objectives v5.0** only. No dump URLs — run `python3 scripts/lint-practice-question-urls.py` after edits.

## Multi-pane sims

Full exam sims (dark web, OpenSSL, VPC) stay in `SEC+_Sim_Hot_Spot/` — not this template.
